videos.headline: Patterson freestyles to avoid the defense and toss TD
videos.description: Ole Miss quarterback Shea Patterson does his best Johnny Manzel impersonation at Kyle Field scrambling to avoid the defense and buying himself just enough time to find Damore'ea Stringfellow for the Rebels touchdown.
